+    /**
+     * Sets the virtual destination on the ConsumerInfo
+     * If this is a VirtualTopic then the destination used will be the actual topic subscribed
+     * to in order to track demand properly
+     *
+     * @param info
+     * @param virtualDestination
+     * @param activeMQDest
